am\nimprovements to the theme without a difficult manual upgrade process.","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":23,"offset":2420},"end":{"line":54,"column":70,"offset":2866}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1,"offset":2180},"end":{"line":54,"column":70,"offset":2866}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"why-themes"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#why-themes","aria-label":"why themes permalink","class":"anchor"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Why Themes?","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":4,"offset":2871},"end":{"line":56,"column":15,"offset":2882}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1,"offset":2868},"end":{"line":56,"column":15,"offset":2882}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Defining themes as the base composition unit of Gatsby sites allows us to start\nsolving a variety of use cases. For example, when a site gets built as\npart of a wider product offering it’s often the case that one team\nwill build out a suite of functionality, including branding elements,\nand the other teams will mostly consume this functionality. Themes\nallow us to distribute this functionality as an npm package and allow\nthe customization of various branding elements through our\n","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1,"offset":2884},"end":{"line":65,"column":1,"offset":3368}}},{"typ